OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with clear periods.
OL,7,FStaying dry overnight but clouding
OL,8,Fover across the southwest later.
OL,9,FStrengthening southwesterly winds
OL,10,Falong the west coast. Cold with some
OL,11,Ffrost.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FWarm in any brightness
OL,14,Falong the Moray coast otherwise
OL,15,Fbecoming rather cloudy. Outbreaks of
OL,16,Frain will spread northeast through the
OL,17,Fday, mainly affecting the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
