OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FCloudy with rain spreading east on
OL,7,FThursday, becoming drier from the west
OL,8,Flater. Dry and bright on Friday and
OL,9,FSaturday. Strong southwesterly winds
OL,10,Facross the far northwest on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
